sentences.english: 52 [Comment From miber]—anything new/interesting for the barbarian or witch doctor?
sentences.chinese: 巫医或者是野蛮人有没有什么新鲜事？

sentences.english: Agence France-Presse said that at least 14 human victims of witch doctors.
sentences.chinese: 法新社说，受害者中至少14人为巫医。

sentences.english: Hank was done brown by a witch doctor.
sentences.chinese: 汉克被巫医弄得皮肤呈棕色。

sentences.english: Though she chose to become a doctor, she said there was ample room for both approaches.
sentences.chinese: 虽然她选择成为医生，但她表示西医和巫医并行不悖。

sentences.english: Some healers say they have given muti to Bafana players, and Mr.
sentences.chinese: 一些巫医说，他们已经将灵药给了南非国家队的球员。

sentences.english: A while ago Gles was a well-known witch-doctor capable of curing even the most horrible wounds.
sentences.chinese: 格雷丝在过去是一位能起死回生的知名巫医。

sentences.english: The witch-doctor has cursed our cattle.
sentences.chinese: 巫医念了咒语想叫我家的牛遭殃。

sentences.english: Flux: i found an axe that my wd couldn’t equip. so i think there’s a lot of it.
sentences.chinese: 我发现了巫医不能装备的斧子。
